author: LEGOGarfield
title: The Orange General Mills LEGO Racer
review: I have owned this since 2009, but did not know how uncommon they were until now. I did not even know their were stickers as I only own this one, and only because it was it a box of cereal my grandparents bought. The top piece of the car has the number 85458 on one part, the number 01-06 somewhere else, and says (c) 2009 LEGO.
